listing.Name: Islais Place
listing.Parking_Information: 22 Parking spaces will be assigned in lottery rank order.
listing.Legal_Disclaimers:
The California Tax Credit Allocation Committee Compliance Manual governs many of the eligibility requirements for this building. Income and assets are calculated by the building staff and appeals are addressed internally by the building. Applicants should inquire with the building contact person listed above for further information about eligibility requirements for this property.


It is also important to note that these units are NOT governed by the San Francisco Rent Ordinance (also known as “rent control”). Among other rules, rents may increase beyond increases allowed under “rent control”.

listing.Credit_Rating:
Credit History (student loans and medical expenses are excluded) 
•	Total unmet credit problems, including government tax liens, 
        within the last three (3) years must not be in excess of $2,500.
•	May not have bankruptcy discharged within the last three (3) 
        years.
•	May not have a total of seven (7) or more unmet credit 
        problems of any value within the last three (3) years.
listing.Eviction_History:
Rental History
•	May not have a judgement against an applicant obtained by the current or previous landlord (no-fault evictions will not count against applicant) within the last three (3) years. 
•	May not have an unmet obligation owed to a previous landlord within the last three (3) years.
•	Applicants must have made timely payments of the last year’s rental payments.
listing.Costs_Not_Included:
Tenants pay electricity (heating, cooking, lighting), telephone, internet and cable. Community Room Reservation Agreement and payment of a cleaning and damage deposit of $300.  Late Fee: $20

Mailbox keys - $50 
Door keys - $50 
Entry card - $50
listing.Amenities: On-Site Laundry Rooms, Elevator, On-Site Professional Management, Parking Spaces, Bike Parking, Children’s Play Area, Courtyard, Community Room with Kitchen.
listing.Accessibility:
Lobby and community room are wheelchair accessible. Building has common area accessible bathrooms and elevators and an accessible multipurpose room. 

Mobility Accessible units have the following modifications: 
Bathroom:
•	Accessible bathtub and controls with clearance for wheelchair
•	Bathtub surround with grab bars
•	Accessible bathroom sink and faucet
•	Accessible medicine cabinet
•	Grab bars at toilet
•	Lowered towel bars and robe hook
Kitchen: 
•	Accessible range 
•	Accessible switch for circulating hood (stove)
•	Kitchen electrical outlets and controls in proper reach range
•	Kitchen cabinets with 34” high countertop and 30” work surface
Living Room/Bedroom:
•	Closet rod and shelf at ADA height (48”)
•	Entry door and door hardware for ADA units include lockset with levers, closer and peepholes.

Hearing Accessible Units have the following modifications:
•	Fire alarm has strobes
•	Doorbell with visual notification
listing.Required_Documents:
o	Completed post lottery application
o	Tenant Income Certification Questionnaire 
o	Latest federal tax return if self-employed
o	Three months of consecutive paystubs if employed. 
o	Latest award letter for Social Security or Supplemental Security Income
o	Latest award letter if receiving unemployment benefits 
o	Court order for child support/alimony 
o	Copy of a driver’s license or state identification per adult 
o	Copy of birth certificate for each minor
o	Copy of social security card for all household members (if applicable)
listing.Smoking_Policy: Smoking is not permitted in any common area; this includes the manager’s office, the community room, hallways, laundry rooms, and offices.
listing.Pet_Policy: Islais Place does not allow pets of any kind. Service and Companion Animals are not considered pets. Please refer to our reasonable accommodation policy.
